text: Mareike Miller (born 3 August 1990) is a German wheelchair basketball player. She won a gold medal at the 2012 Summer Paralympics and silver medal at the 2016 Summer Paralympics. She played at the 2014 Women's World Wheelchair Basketball Championship and 2018 Wheelchair Basketball World Championship. == References == Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Paralympic gold medalists for Germany Category:Paralympic silver medalists for Germany Category:German wheelchair basketball players
